婆私下和我妈妈说，我一天老想工作不管家里。我很气愤，为什么没人想想我呢？我也担心自己40岁失业，我也想成长。 3、我想证明我自己的价值不是在家做家务，我不会做饭，收拾屋子能力不是很好，在我因生孩子、疫情在家呆着的那几个月，婆婆也说过我家里和工作一事无成这样的话，我挺想证明自己的。 4、我老公现在是支持我的，但是，我也是被他之前说我“就是不行”激怒了，所以才会去找上海的这次机会，也是想证明自己。 5、33岁一个人去上海，错过孩子的成长，是否是值得的？孩子在家跟老人们待久了会不会对成长影响很大？女性该如何平衡家庭和工作？如果我这次去了，蝴蝶效应导致婚姻破裂是否值得？"}, "attached_info": "Cj8IkLvRxoOmit9YEAMaCDU5NjA4OTE5IPO30P8FMBM49wNAFHIJNDM3OTg2Njg1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=", "detail_text": "270 万热度", "trend": 0, "debut": false, "children": [{"type": "answer", "thumbnail": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-da9b509b182499c3d3a71146aad78a7f_b.jpg"}]}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "21_1610301600.4837227", "card_id": "Q_300989157", "target": {"id": 300989157, "title": "大家喝过奶味最浓最好喝的牛奶是什么？", "url": "https://api.zhihu.com/questions/300989157", "type": "question", "created": 1541141148, "answer_count": 2417, "follower_count": 26104, "author": {"type": "people", "user_type": "people", "id": "0", "url_token": "", "url": "", "name": "用户", "headline": "", "avatar_url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"}, "bound_topic_ids": [361, 9080, 97149], "comment_count": 106, "is_following": false, "excerpt": ""}, "attached_info": "CkAIkLvRxoOmit9YEAMaCDI5MTYyODYwIJzl794FMGo4+MsBQBVyCTMwMDk4OTE1N3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA", "detail_text": "263 万热度", "trend": 0, "debut": false, "children": [{"type": "answer", "thumbnail": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-2287552783c78df4d649486fbe3d4735_720w.png"}]}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "22_1610301600.484125", "card_id": "Q_437767472", "target": {"id": 437767472, "title": "如何看待王者荣耀S22赛季的大版本更新？", "url": "https://api.zhihu.com/questions/437767472", "type": "question", "created": 1609717103, "answer_count": 89, "follower_count": 380, "author": {"type": "people", "user_type": "people", "id": "0", "url_token": "", "url": "", "name": "用户", "headline": "", "avatar_url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"}, "bound_topic_ids": [11210, 163534, 183735, 390328, 404003], "comment_count": 4, "is_fo